<para>Wi-Fi power save timeout. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This is the time out to wait after sending a TX packet before going back to power save (in ms) to receive any replies from the AP. Zero means this feature is disabled.</para>
<para>It&apos;s a tradeoff between power consumption and latency. </para>
